abstract: John Daly has good start at Pebble Beach National Pro-Am with seven-under-par 65.
lead_paragraph: Daly played bogey-free for a seven-under-par 65 and was one shot behind J. B. Holmes and Justin Hicks at the Pebble Beach National Pro-Am.

headline.main: John Daly Starts Well at Pebble Beach
headline.print_headline: Daly Starts Well at Pebble Beach
